  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Fuel tank removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Fire is strictly prohibited. ​",
        "Removal should be performed with the engine stopped and the battery (-) terminal disconnected. ​"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Gasoline that has been drained should be stored in a safe place."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Fuel pressure Removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000474",
          "label": "Fuel pressure Removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Fuel Extraction",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000476",
          "label": "Fuel Extraction",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Always drain at least half of the gasoline before starting work.",
        "The fuel pump must be left disconnected."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Lift Up",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "G000319",
          "label": "Lift Up",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. Propeller shaft removal (4WD vehicles)",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000615",
          "label": "Propeller shaft removal (4WD vehicles)",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "5. Fuel tank guard pipe removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "489_3.0_jpn_11582618_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "489_3.0_jpn_11582619_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the fuel tank guard pipe (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "6. Suction joint removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "489_3.0_jpn_11582620_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the suction joint (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "7. Fuel filler tube, breather tube Disconnect"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "489_3.0_jpn_11582621_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect the fuel filler tube (A) and breather tube (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "8. Fuel Vent Tube Disconnect"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "489_3.0_jpn_11582622_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "489_3.0_jpn_11582623_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect the fuel vent tube (B) from the canister (A). Release the fuel vent tube securing clip (C). (4WD vehicles)"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "9. Fuel tank removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "489_3.0_jpn_11582624_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "489_3.0_jpn_11582625_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Support the fuel tank (A) with a transmission jack, etc., and remove the fuel tank."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "10. Fuel tank protector removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "489_3.0_jpn_11582626_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "489_3.0_jpn_11582627_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the fuel tank protector (A) from the fuel tank."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "11. Installation Precautions"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Installation is the reverse of the removal procedure.",
      "refs": [
