    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "12. Maintenance Lid Installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "489_3.0_jpn_11582628_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Bent Tube (A), Connect the quick-connect fuel tube (B). Connect the coupler (C). When the 12V battery negative (-) terminal is connected and the ignition is turned to the ON mode (never turn the starter), the fuel pump operates for about 2 seconds to increase the fuel pressure in the fuel line system. Repeat this operation 2-3 times and check for fuel leaks in each part of the fuel piping system. Install the maintenance lid (D).",
